        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="mathorcup¼">2023��mathorcup��¼</h1><h2 id="section">4��13��12:00��¼</h2><p>����������⣬���Լ���ѡ��C�⡣</p><p>C��ؼ������㣺<strong>�������أ�����</strong>����ӹ���ɺ�ֱ�ף�����81������·1049����ÿ�ջ�����Ŀ���������������ͼ���⣬����ͼ����Ҳ����ΪĿ�꺯��������</p><p>��վ��㼯��<span class="math inline">\(v_i\)</span>�� ���߱߼���<spanclass="math inline">\(e_{ij}\)</span>(�г��ֲ���)��</p><p><span class="math inline">\(x_{ij} = 0 �� 1\)</span>����ʾ�Ƿ�ѡ��������·�ߣ� <span class="math inline">\(x_{ij} \neqx_{ji}\)</span></p><p>�Ż�Լ����������Ӫ�ɱ��������ӪЧ�ʣ�ֵ��˼������</p><table style="width:8%;"><colgroup><col style="width: 8%" /></colgroup><tbody><tr class="odd"><td>## 4��13��20:00��¼</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>A�������</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>N�����+N����ֵ ��������<span class="math inline">\(S\)</span> =������Ϣ���� �� ������ʧ</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>�����ʽ�Ϊ<span class="math inline">\(W\)</span>��������Ϣ������Ϊ<spanclass="math inline">\(c\)</span>���������ֿ�ѡ��Ϊ<spanclass="math inline">\(i\)</span>��<span class="math inline">\(1 &lt;= i&lt;= 100\)</span>������ֵѡ��Ϊ<spanclass="math inline">\(j\)</span>��<span class="math inline">\(1 &lt;= j&lt;= 10\)</span>����<spanclass="math inline">\(t_{ij}\)</span>��ʾΪͨ���ʣ�<spanclass="math inline">\(h_{ij}\)</span>��ʾ�����ʡ�</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>��һ�ʣ�</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>���ѡ���i���������ֿ��ĵ�j����ֵѡ��</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>��ͨ���ʣ�<span class="math inline">\(t = t_{ij}\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>�ܻ����ʣ�<span class="math inline">\(h = h_{ij}\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>������Ϣ���룺<span class="math inline">\(W_1 = W \times c \times t\times (1 - h)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>������ʧ��<span class="math inline">\(W_2 = W \times t \timesh\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>�������룺<span class="math inline">\(S = W_1 - W_2\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>�����ã�<span class="math inline">\(S = W \times c \times t_{ij}\times (1 - h_{ij}) - W \times t_{ij} \times h_{ij}\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>�����</td></tr><tr class="even"><td><span class="math inline">\(x_i = \left\{ \begin{aligned} 0 \quad&amp; \text{��ѡ���i���������ֿ�} \\ 1 \quad &amp;\text{ѡ���i���������ֿ�}\end{aligned}\right.\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td><span class="math inline">\(y_j = \left\{ \begin{aligned} 0 \quad&amp; \text{��ѡ���j����ֵ} \\ 1 \quad &amp;\text{ѡ���j����ֵ}\end{aligned}\right.\)</span></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>Ŀ�꺯����<span class="math inline">\(Max \quad S = W \times c \times(t_{ij} \times (1 - h_{ij}) \times x_i \times y_j) - W \times (t_{ij}\times h_{ij} \times x_i \times y_j)\)</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>Լ��������</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>1. <span class="math display">\[\sum_{i=1}^{100}x_i = 1\]</span> 2.<span class="math display">\[\sum_{j=1}^{10}y_j = 1\]</span></td></tr><tr class="odd"><td>## 4��13��23:00��¼</td></tr><tr class="even"><td>���Ѹ��ĵ�һ����룺</td></tr><tr class="odd"><td><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> pandas <span class="keyword">as</span> pd</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ��ȡ����</span></span><br><span class="line">df = pd.read_csv(<span class="string">&quot;����1��data_100.csv&quot;</span>)  <span class="comment"># ��ȡ����</span></span><br><span class="line">t_data = df.iloc[:, <span class="number">0</span>::<span class="number">2</span>].values.T.flatten()  <span class="comment"># �����������ֿ���ͨ����</span></span><br><span class="line">h_data = df.iloc[:, <span class="number">1</span>::<span class="number">2</span>].values.T.flatten()  <span class="comment"># �����������ֿ��Ļ�����</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># ÿʮ��Ϊһ��</span></span><br><span class="line">t = [t_data[i:i+<span class="number">10</span>] <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="built_in">len</span>(t_data), <span class="number">10</span>)]</span><br><span class="line">h = [h_data[i:i+<span class="number">10</span>] <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="built_in">len</span>(h_data), <span class="number">10</span>)]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">L = <span class="number">1000000</span>   <span class="comment">#������ʽ�Ϊ1000000Ԫ</span></span><br><span class="line">r = <span class="number">0.08</span>    <span class="comment">#�����д�����Ϣ������Ϊ8%</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">ls = []</span><br><span class="line">max_data = -<span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;inf&#x27;</span>)  <span class="comment"># ��ʼ�� max_data Ϊ������</span></span><br><span class="line">max_i, max_j = <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>       <span class="comment"># ��ʼ�� max_i �� max_j Ϊ 0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">100</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        W = L*r*(t[i][j])*(<span class="number">1</span>-(h[i][j]))</span><br><span class="line">        Q = L*(t[i][j])*(h[i][j])</span><br><span class="line">        S_data = W - Q</span><br><span class="line">        ls.append(S_data)  <span class="comment"># �� S_data ���ӵ��б� ls ��</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># print(ls)</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> S_data &gt; max_data:  <span class="comment"># �����ǰ�� S_data ֵ���� max_data</span></span><br><span class="line">            max_data = S_data  <span class="comment"># �� max_data ����Ϊ��ǰ S_data ֵ</span></span><br><span class="line">            max_i, max_j = i, j  <span class="comment"># �� max_i �� max_j ����Ϊ��Ӧ������ֵ</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;���� S_data ֵΪ <span class="subst">&#123;max_data&#125;</span>����Ӧ������������ֿ�Ϊ <span class="subst">&#123;max_i&#125;</span>����Ӧ�������ֵΪ <span class="subst">&#123;max_j+<span class="number">1</span>&#125;</span>&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></td></tr><tr class="even"><td>���гɹ��������ı����ݺ�����ı�������֪���ǲ��Ƿ������Ӽ��㣿</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="section-1">4��14��8:00��¼</h2><p>�ڶ���</p><p>��֪ѡ��Ϊ�������ֿ�1��2��3.</p><p>��ͨ���ʣ�<span class="math inline">\(t = (t_{1j} \times y_j) \times(t_{2j} \times y_j) \times (t_{3j} \times y_j)\)</span></p><p>�ܻ����ʣ�<span class="math inline">\(h = \frac{1}{3}[(h_{1j} \timesy_j) + (h_{2j} \times y_j) + (h_{3j} \times y_j)]\)</span></p><p>������Ϣ���룺<span class="math inline">\(W_1 = W \times c \times t\times (1 - h)\)</span></p><p>������ʧ��<span class="math inline">\(W_2 = W \times t \timesh\)</span></p><p>�������룺<span class="math inline">\(S = W_1 - W_2\)</span></p><p>Ŀ�꺯����<span class="math inline">\(Max \quad S = W \times c \times t\times (1 - h) - W \times t \times h\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(y_j = \left\{  \begin{aligned}  0 \quad&amp; \text{��ѡ���j����ֵ} \\  1 \quad &amp;\text{ѡ���j����ֵ}\end{aligned}\right.\)</span></p><h2 id="section-2">4��14��23:00��¼</h2><h3 id="ģͼ">ģ�ͼ���</h3><p>Ϊ�˹�����Ϊ��ȷ����ѧģ�ͣ����ĸ���ʵ������������º������裺</p><p>1.�����������ʽ�Ϊ��������Ϊ������2.����ÿ���������ֿ����໥�����������ţ�ÿ�ſ���ÿ����ֵҲͬ���໥�����������š�3.����������������ֻ�������Ϣ����ͻ�����ʧ�йء�4.�������д�����Ϣ������Ϊ4%~10%����䶯��ģ���������������Ӱ�죬����Ϊ������</p><h2 id="section-3">4��15��15:20��¼</h2><p>����һ�����ͨ���ʽϸߣ��������������ͨ���ʻ������½�������ı仯��Խ���仯����Ӱ�졣</p><p>��ģ�͵���ȱ�㣺</p><p><strong>�ŵ㣺</strong></p><p>1.ʹ����QUBOģ�ͷ������Ӽ����������⣬�ܹ��ӿ���������ٶȣ�Ϊ�����Ŵ������ṩ��ݣ���������������</p><p>2.����ģ��ͨ�ÿ��ŷ��ȸߣ����ڲ�������ѡ���������������</p><p><strong>ȱ�㣺</strong></p><p>1.ģ�͹��ڼ��ף�ʵ�������д�����Ϣ�����ʵı仯Ҳ��Ӱ�������������ֿ���ѡ�񣬶����������ֿ����ܵ���෽���Ӱ�죬������ʷ�����¼�ȡ�</p><p>2.�����д���ͨ���ʵ�Լ�����ǲ���ȫ�棬�����������ȡ���ڽ���˵ĸ������ü�¼��������Դ���ȶ����Լ�������������������ء�</p><hr /><h2 id="section-4">4��15��23:45��¼</h2><p>����ͳһ���ţ�������ʲô����Ҫ�����ű���Ķ�����Ҫ���� �ܣ�</p><p><span class="math inline">\(L\)</span> : ���ʽ�</p><p><span class="math inline">\(r\)</span> : ������Ϣ������</p><p><span class="math inline">\(i\)</span> : ��i�����ÿ�</p><p><span class="math inline">\(j\)</span> : ��j����ֵ</p><p><span class="math inline">\(t_{i,j}\)</span> :��i�����ÿ��ĵ�j����ֵ��ͨ����</p><p><span class="math inline">\(h_{i,j}\)</span> :��i�����ÿ��ĵ�j����ֵ�Ļ�����</p><p><span class="math inline">\(x_{i,j}\)</span> :�Ƿ�ѡ���i���������ֿ���j����ֵ</p><p><span class="math inline">\(W\)</span> : ������Ϣ����</p><p><span class="math inline">\(Q\)</span> : ������ʧ</p><p>�ڶ��ʣ�</p><p>ͨ������<spanclass="math inline">\(t_{1,a}��t_{2,b}��t_{3,c}\)</span></p><p>��������<spanclass="math inline">\(h_{1,a}��h_{2,b}��h_{3,c}\)</span></p><p><span class="math inline">\(a, b, c\)</span> :�ֱ��ʾ��һ�����������������ֿ�����ֵ</p><hr /><h2 id="section-5">4��16��10:30��¼</h2><p>������ģ�ͽ���</p><p>���100�ŵ������ѡ�������������ֿ�Ϊ��<span class="math inline">\(\alpha,\beta, \gamma\)</span>���������ֿ���������ѡ�����ֵ�ֱ�Ϊ<spanclass="math inline">\(n, m, l\)</span>�������ǵ�ͨ���ʿ��Ա�ʾΪ<spanclass="math inline">\(t_{\alpha, n}��t_{\beta, m}��t_{\gamma,l}\)</span>�������ʿ��Ա�ʾΪ<span class="math inline">\(h_{\alpha,n}��h_{\beta, m}��h_{\gamma, l}\)</span></p><p>���Ը�ģ���е���ͨ���ʿ����޸�Ϊ��<span class="math inline">\(t = (t_{\alpha,n} \times x_{\alpha, n}) \times (t_{\beta, m} \times x_{\beta, m})\times (t_{\gamma, l} \times x_{\gamma, l})\)</span></p><p>ͬ�����ܻ����ʿ��޸�Ϊ��<span class="math inline">\(h =\frac{1}{3}[(h_{\alpha, n} \times x_{\alpha, n}) + (h_{\beta, m} \timesx_{\beta, m}) + (h_{\gamma, l} \times x_{\gamma, l})]\)</span></p><p>Ϊ��ʹģ����ֵѡȡ�������������ʵ���Լ��������ͨ��ǰ���ʼ������֪����һ����ϵ��������ֿ�ͨ������70%<sub>90%֮�䣬����������������ֿ�ͨ������30%</sub>90%֮�䣬���Զ�ͨ���ʽ��к�����Լ�������ܻ��ʵĸı���������뼸��û�иı䡣�����ⶨͨ����Ϊ50%�����Ϊ<spanclass="math inline">\(\pm 5\%\)</span>����ͨ���ʷ�ΧΪ<spanclass="math inline">\(45\% \sim 55\%\)</span>��</p><p>����Լ������Ϊ��<span class="math inline">\(0.45 &lt; t &lt;0.55\)</span></p><p>������Ϣ���룺<span class="math inline">\(W_1 = W \times c \times t\times (1 - h)\)</span></p><p>������ʧ��<span class="math inline">\(W_2 = W \times t \timesh\)</span></p><p>�������룺<span class="math inline">\(S = W_1 - W_2\)</span></p><p>Ŀ�꺯����<span class="math inline">\(Max \quad S = W \times c \times t\times (1 - h) - W \times t \times h\)</span></p><p>���������������</p><p>��������Ȼ��������ǰ���ʵĻ���ģ�͡�</p><p>��100���������ֿ����ѡ�����ţ���Ҫ���������ԣ�����ֻ���ĳ�����������ֿ���Ч��Ϊ��ʹģ����ֵѡȡ�������������ʵ���Լ��������ͨ��ǰ���ʼ������֪����һ����ϵ��������ֿ�ͨ������70%<sub>90%֮�䣬����������������ֿ�ͨ������30%</sub>90%֮�䣬���Զ�ͨ���ʽ��к�����Լ�������ܻ��ʵĸı���������뼸��û�иı䡣����ճ������Ŵ�֪ʶ�����Լ��������������ֿ�ͨ����Ϊ50%��</p><p>�ٽ�������ɵ�ģ��ת��ΪQUBOģ�ͣ���ʹ��Python������⣬�������������롣</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
